    </article>
    <article class="portfolio__intro--projects">
      <div class="projects__container">
        <div class="projects__card" id="project">
          <h2 class="article__title">Clonado de pagina web</h2>
          <div class="project__img">
            <Image src={photo} alt="Imagen proyecto" width={400} />
          </div>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolore, aspernatur? Illum, nam consequatur molestias suscipit iure incidunt consequuntur similique aperiam repellendus ipsa aut quaerat neque excepturi temporibus. Optio, itaque corporis.</p>
